Package lawnlayer

Class Entity

  • java.lang.Object
    • lawnlayer.GameObject
      • lawnlayer.Entity
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Enemy, Player
    public abstract class Entity
extends GameObject
    An abstract subclass of GameObject governing the behaviours of all entities in the game. Entities include the Player and all Enemy types.

      • isOverlapping

        public boolean isOverlapping​(GameObject other)
        Checks whether this Entity is overlapping the specified GameObject 'other'.

        Checking mechanism for overlap depends on this Entity's implementation of the abstract methods which check for vertical and horizontal overlaps.

        Parameters:
        other - the GameObject to be checked against for overlap
        Returns:
        true if this Entity overlaps with 'other'
        See Also:
        isOverlappingHorizontally(GameObject), isOverlappingVertically(GameObject)

      • isOverlapping

        public boolean isOverlapping​(TileList otherTiles)
        Checks whether this Entity is overlapping any of the tiles in the specified TileList 'otherTiles'.

        Checking mechanism for overlap depends on this Entity's implementation of the abstract methods which check for vertical and horizontal overlaps.

        Parameters:
        otherTiles - the TileList to be checked against for overlap
        Returns:
        true if this Entity overlaps with at least one tile inside 'otherTiles'
        See Also:
        isOverlapping(GameObject)
